Paper: hep-th/9812034

Date: 1998-12-03

Title: Black Holes and Calogero Models

Authors: G.W. Gibbons and P.K. Townsend

Comments: Revtex 5pp. Revision includes improved discussion of entropy and

includes an additional referenceJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B454 (1999) 187-192

We argue that the large $n$ limit of the $n$-particle $SU(1,1|2)$superconformal Calogero model provides a microscopic description of the extremeReissner-Nordstr{\"o}m black hole in the near-horizon limit.